{"id": "1184423968707465237", "channel_id": "1184220538655223939", "type": 0, "author_id": "937726505188995113", "author_name": "meow51103", "author_bot": false, "content": "第三\n啟靈越高 角色用起來越順手\n選好界域後 看誰起靈最高\n優先以他為主來配對", "timestamp": "2023-12-13T09:17:59.673000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184220538655223939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "那些新手期我踩過的坑", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
