{"id": "1184428675471507556", "channel_id": "1184220538655223939", "type": 0, "author_id": "937726505188995113", "author_name": "meow51103", "author_bot": false, "content": "第五\n體力恢復好慢 不夠用\n主角等級一直卡著\n每天可以買前三次體力\n50 100 100 150⋯⋯\nCP質都很高", "timestamp": "2023-12-13T09:36:41.853000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2023-12-14T02:34:09.464000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "💖", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [{"id": "1184428675207278602", "filename": "IMG_1593.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1361552, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184220538655223939/1184428675207278602/IMG_1593.png?ex=69cb95a9&is=69ca4429&hm=f3ec5bf95c6238865f36935e2670b7619d1cca332ee83e806d0e9e8c6e9bec1e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184220538655223939", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "那些新手期我踩過的坑", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854"]}
{"id": "1184413785537138688", "channel_id": "1184413785537138688", "type": 0, "author_id": "937726505188995113", "author_name": "meow51103", "author_bot": false, "content": "Boss打我300 我反她751傷害+300毒😏快樂\n\n凱有三啟時歡迎善加利用\n反擊一直疊一直疊\n防禦一直疊一直疊\n都不知道誰是boss\n\n核心人物 凱（粉毛）三啟\n珊命輪戴傷痛之鰭（因為她防禦最高）\n奧（防禦數值也高）\n三位的1費防禦牌看到能丟就丟\n你會發現反擊一直漲📈\n\n啟靈優先 凱\n凱耗點加反擊、回血\n\n奧的穿刺可以賣掉\n\n命輪部分 跟防禦有關的都帶上", "timestamp": "2023-12-13T08:37:31.816000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1184413786086572062", "filename": "IMG_1578.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2159283, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184413785537138688/1184413786086572062/IMG_1578.png?ex=69cb87cb&is=69ca364b&hm=e7f4069a63b76626d6d3d74d428c12dbab25122e68a84c5f44ec91520b690fd0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184413785537138688", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "你粉毛三啟？那來看看這個隊伍👉深海盾反", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1174179680056791130", "1174180524034637854", "1174179716706619494", "1174179700470460447"]}
